                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.4131/144: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Atherton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-02-28T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 28, 1936—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>70. Your 79, February 26, 7 p.m., and 81, February 28, 1 p.m. Do you believe that
                    Eden had talked with Runciman on subject of my instruction 1130 of February 13
                    before Runciman made the speech reported in your 81? I am very anxious to have
                    any information which might become available to you relating to this
                    subject.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
